msg the warrior lion heart is a film directed by gurmeet ram rahim singh and his daughter honeypreet insan .   the film starring gurmeet ram rahim singh , is a story of a medieval warrior fighting against aliens for the honour of his land .   the movie premiered on 6 october in delhi and was released on 7 october in hindi , with dubs in tamil , telugu , malayalam and english .   singh is credited with work in thirty film departments , including choreography , editing , make-up and hair design , background scoring , and prop design .   the film has been highly criticized as a propaganda film by several critics .